strings: <voice_0x01000F04><se_def>Angelo: What's this? It's barely even light yet!
<voice_0x01000F05><se_high>Jessica: Grrrr...!

<voice_0x01000F06><se_high>Jessica: What's that noise?
Are we under attack or something?
<voice_0x01000F07><se_low>Yangus: Wot's goin' on, eh?
<voice_0x01000F08><se_low>Yangus: The 'orse-princess don't sound too 'appy this mornin'...
<voice_0x01000F09><se_def>Prince Charmles: Come on! Giddy-up! Do as I say!
<voice_0x01000F0A><se_def>Prince Charmles: Giddy-up! Go!
<voice_0x01000F0B><se_def>Prince Charmles: Listen to me, you stupid beast!

<voice_0x01000F0C><se_low>King Trode: Prince! Please restrain yourself! Medea is...
I mean...
<voice_0x01000F0D><se_low>King Trode: My horse isn't accustomed to being ridden!

<voice_0x01000F0E><se_low>King Trode: Come on now! Down from my horse at once,
you fat oaf!
<voice_0x01000F0F><se_def>Prince Charmles: Shut up! I'll show you how to break in a horse!

<voice_0x01000F10><se_def>Prince Charmles: Stupid animal!
Maybe a little pain will teach you!
<voice_0x01000F11><se_def>Prince Charmles: Waaaaah!
<voice_0x01000F12><se_def>Prince Charmles: Calm down!
<voice_0x01000F13><se_def>Prince Charmles: Stop bucking! Stop! I'm going to fall!
<voice_0x01000F14><se_def>Prince Charmles: Whoa...!
<voice_0x01000F15><se_def>Prince Charmles: I'll whip some manners into you!
<voice_0x01000F16><se_def>Prince Charmles: You stubborn beast! You should be honoured to have a taste of my crop! I'll teach you some proper respect for your rider!

<voice_0x01000F17><se_low>King Trode: That's MY horse!
Stop this at once!

<voice_0x01000F18><se_low>King Trode: I simply cannot allow you to harass her
any further. If you must strike something,
strike me instead!

<voice_0x01000F19><se_def>Prince Charmles: So the horse is that important to you?
Fine. Your wish is granted.
Prepare to accept her punishment!
<voice_0x01000F1A><se_low>Yangus: Oi! Guv!
<voice_0x01000F1B><se_low>Yangus: We got one! We got one!
<voice_0x01000F1C><se_low>Yangus: Hahh...hahh...
<voice_0x01000F1D><se_low>Yangus: I was pickin' me nos<endash>

<voice_0x01000F1E><se_low>Yangus: Er, I mean, I was pickin' me some flowers,
when I saw it! A bloomin' giant...
<voice_0x01000F1F><se_low>Yangus: ...one. One o' them lizards!

<voice_0x01000F20><se_def>Prince Charmles: Did you hear that?
It's the cry of an Argon lizard!

<voice_0x01000F21><se_def>Prince Charmles: Forget the stupid horse!
We've got to catch that lizard!
